                                <Label Text="It's a film worth watching . There's a lot of information about the disorder -' Dissociative Identity Disorder' like how a person or even any animal facing the disorder can have different iq, different health issues and all together several personality for each character , he/she thinks them to be. But, the movie inflicts fear rather than spreading awareness,thus the movie could be shown in a more practical and positive way that could lighten up the people to help others. &#10;" TextColor="#37383b" FontSize="15" CharacterSpacing="0.2" />

