                                    <Label Text="Lilikoi McCreadie &#10;2 years ago" FontAttributes="Bold" TextColor="Black" FontSize="13" CharacterSpacing="0.5"/>
                                    <Image Source="https://i.ibb.co/Bs7bnky/5.png" WidthRequest="70"/>
                                </StackLayout>
                                <Label Text="Split was a really good movie. I find it fascinating that James Mcavoy was able to portray so many characters, he was also able to switch in seconds. It was so easy to tell which person he was with not only his voices he did for each character, but also the way his posture was as well. Each of these 9 personas portrayed in the film were completely different despite being played by the same actor. &#10;" TextColor="#37383b" FontSize="15" CharacterSpacing="0.2" />

