                                    <Label Text="Oblivion Approaches &#10;a year ago" FontAttributes="Bold" TextColor="Black" FontSize="13" CharacterSpacing="0.5"/>
                                    <Image Source="https://i.ibb.co/Bs7bnky/5.png" WidthRequest="70"/>
                                </StackLayout>
                                <Label Text="It's a great movie of how the mind works or how it fails to work.  It kind of explains the different ways or maybe more accurately weird ways people see and interpret things. James McAvoy has done a perfect job for the different personalities. &#10;The 9 year old dancing is entertainingly creepy. &#10;" TextColor="#37383b" FontSize="15" CharacterSpacing="0.2" />

