                                </StackLayout>
                                <Label Text="Like pretty much every other M Night Shyamalan movie, SPLIT is an extremely under-rated movie. You think Heath Ledger was good in The Dark Knight, James McAvoy in SPLIT is Phenomenal and deserved the Oscar that year and was unfortunately Robbed. &#10;" TextColor="#37383b" FontSize="15" CharacterSpacing="0.2" />

